====Verb====
{{en-verb|chat|t|ing}}
[[image:Wikimania 2009 - Chatting (3).jpg|thumb|Two people '''chatting'''. (1) (2)]]

# To be [[engage]]d in informal [[conversation]].
#: ''She '''chatted''' with her friend in the cafe.''
#: ''I like to '''chat''' over a coffee with a friend.''
# To talk more than a few words.
#: ''I met my old friend in the street, so we '''chatted''' for a while.''
# To exchange [[text]] or [[voice]] [[message]]s in [[real time]] through a [[computer]] [[network]], as if having a [[face-to-face]] conversation.
#: ''Do you want to '''chat''' online later?''

